PRIVACY POLICY FOR OHR

Last updated: [15.07.2025]

Ohr ("we", "our", or "us") operates the Ohr podcast app. This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our app.

INFORMATION WE COLLECT
- Podcast subscriptions (stored locally on your device)
- Episode playback history (stored locally on your device)
- Downloaded episodes (stored locally on your device)

We do NOT collect:
- Personal identification information
- Location data
- Contact information
- Analytics or tracking data

DATA STORAGE
All data is stored locally on your device. We do not have servers that collect or store your personal information.

THIRD-PARTY SERVICES
- We use the iTunes Search API to search for podcasts
- Podcast RSS feeds are accessed directly from podcast publishers

CHILDREN'S PRIVACY
Our app does not address anyone under the age of 4. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 4.

CHANGES TO THIS POLICY
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

CONTACT US
If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: lukas@studiopizzaparty.com
